originalText.text: I have to admit, I was really nervous about getting headshots done. I was seriously worried that getting a "good shot" just wasn't possible for me, since I don't consider myself photogenic. But, Jamiya's easy going personality and amazing tech/lighting set up did the trick! With literally only one shot taken, I felt it was already better than I had ever had taken before. I am so pleased with my selection of professional head shots. Thank you, Jamiya! I will be coming back with my son for his headshots soon!

originalText.text:
I chose Jamiya partly based on reading these reviews, so I'm happy to contribute mine. This was a great experience, and I couldn't be more happy with the result. I invested in adding a stylist and, between the two of them, I could tell I was working with real pros who knew what they were doing.
Jamiya is super chill and happy to work with you to make you comfortable. I brought several jackets to try on to see which worked best, and he even offered to try them with different backdrops to see the effect. His expertise on everything from styling to lighting put me at ease, and his easy-going personality made the whole experience pleasant and fun, rather than scary.
I'm thrilled to have new headshots that truly reflect my personality and where I am professionally today.

originalText.text: Jamiya is the most helpful and considerate photographer I have yet to work with. He cares so much and really wants to see you win. He helped me pick out my outfits and divide up my looks, and made sure I was happy with each look before moving onto the next. He is also super nice and fun to shoot with! I will go back to Jamiya for any headshots I need in the future !!

originalText.text: Jamiya was excellent to work with. I am not used to having my photo taken professionally and he set a great tone for me to feel really comfortable. I also loved that we were able to look at the photos as we went so I could adjust accordingly per his suggestions and my taste! He took so many options so there was plenty to pick from in the end. All around great experience. Thank you, Jamiya!

originalText.text: Jamiya was great to work with for my corporate headshot. He gives clear instructions for the prep and total time in there was 15 mins. He took 50+ shots and then he emailed me them for touch up and selection. A+ definitely recommend!
